{"tid":1734603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"圍而不攻 必有所謀","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:03:03.000Z","uid":305997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"978b2c8008d3ee8105a423ad6db27e93101a5a84","tid":1734603,"uid":305997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"睇開三國的人都知道，圍城而唔進攻，除左斷絕糧草外，可能有其他目的：<br />\n<br />\n1. 等待援軍，一舉殲滅<br />\n2. 圍魏救趙，分散注意<br />\n3. 以逸待勞，重兵防守<br />\n<br />\n手足唔係condom，但請保持冷靜分析。"},{"pid":"72fdd6a6c0846669dd8c3bc45b0f6be29172c253","tid":1734603,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=c4280cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: gold;\"> /task3</span> <br />\n<br />\n最新Task分類<br />\n/task1: 法案、抗爭活動<br />\n/task2: BNO、中國、其他香港議題<br />\n/task3: !!!! #PolyU !!!!<br />\n/task4: 日韓德任務"},{"pid":"60e472136e8d4d92f05b61a8ea633556b42c1a00","tid":1734603,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"好似東德咁都夠死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb62d9323c0750e8fc6100bc24a5f274936cce8c","tid":1734603,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"分析: 唯一救埋大方法 -- 開花<br />\n<br />\n對家優勢:<br />\n武器精良<br />\n<br />\n對家缺點:<br />\n只有不足1萬防暴<br />\n唔敢入校園(圍而不攻斷吾糧草，但24小時內仲安全)<br />\n現時大部分武器，人手都集中於九龍<br />\n<br />\n結論: 人家有槍，一個可打100個，但係大型武器(eg水炮車)都集中於埋大，但其他地方(如狗聯辨，或各大狗屋)是最脆弱，利用快閃優勢，只要威脅到其他春袋，對家就要分兵離開埋大"}]}